{"id": "1252664028401111145", "channel_id": "1252664028401111145", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "基本收入每個月2.7W固定量，但碎片+命輪的基本消費3.9W，嚴重入不敷出。\n各項活動本人積極參與，但仍無法補足這個差額，期可開發獲取管道。\n註：沉澱兌換就別說了吧，小弟資本有限，要來去換通用碎片+命輪...", "timestamp": "2024-06-18T16:39:37.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252664028401111145", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融蝕之珠獲取管道不足", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1252565827769602048", "channel_id": "1252565827769602048", "type": 0, "author_id": "1202091901210345503", "author_name": "qoshs", "author_bot": false, "content": "先叠甲，我并没有不满意现版本深海的核心触腕机制，只是不了解触腕的双暴计算逻辑，勿喷，要喷也轻点。\n         因为只有开服玩了几星期深海，之后就转了，因为官方对深海可玩性的改善，正好借着弥利亚姆的上架，想试试深海，可苦于太久不玩深海，导致体验不佳。希望弥萨格大学的高管们和各位深海界域的学长们能指点学弟一下。<:flop:1236937860922343466> <:flop:1236937860922343466> <:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2024-06-18T10:09:24.888000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1252565828029644912", "filename": "Screenshot_20240618_180157_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 238960, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1252565827769602048/1252565828029644912/Screenshot_20240618_180157_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=6a005954&is=69ff07d4&hm=256cbe8ba38cdaab268e0f1dddcf879b8a17b826fd26c5c353354d5ec43533aa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252565827769602048", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "鄙人对深海触腕伤害的暴击率和暴击伤害部分还是有点不明白。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
