{"id": "1252507832180543519", "channel_id": "1252507832180543519", "type": 0, "author_id": "1220321436611252265", "author_name": "1021083", "author_bot": false, "content": "你活动也就14天，我觉得你完全可以推过关卡之后，每天打一次就能重现而且第二天重置，这样比较好，然后第七天成就完成结束后就是不用挑战就能重现，这样比较利于萌新刷体力需要重复打劝退", "timestamp": "2024-06-18T06:18:57.662000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252507832180543519", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "活动挑战建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
